{
  "stem": "1857.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 314.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And while they were doing, they were cutting us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they were doing it on purpose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then they ran us into the showers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they gave us some kind of a compound to wash with, which was not soap.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But once we put it on, on the wounds that we had, it wasn't burning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we had heard about showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we were apprehensive to see what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And when the water came out, it was the greatest of reliefs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "From the showers, they ran us naked and wet into a barrack, where they were throwing clothing at us-- shoes and stripe suits-- disregarding the size or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then they took us to another barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we were putting on this clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I had pants that I couldn't close they were so small.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were like shorts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My shoes were too small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But it was close to the night already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we were all going to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how did we sleep?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The barrack was for 200 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they put in 700 people there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were all sitting with spread eagle, into each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is how we spent the first night, the second night, the third night, the fourth night, the fifth night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at night, while people were asleep, we used to walk over bodies and start exchanging the clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So on the fourth, fifth day, everybody had shoes his own size.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because if I swiped somebody's shoes that were larger, and somebody got my shoes that needed a smaller size-- so eventually it equalized.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the day, they made us-- our barrack was right across the street from the crematorium, which was intimidating.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the day, we were standing outside, just doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
